{"tid":1865887,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗連儂牆事件　有遇襲者肋骨斷裂","createTime":"2020-02-06T12:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T12:38:02.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"989ca787faf3643c1e2ac9a83451c822098b9150","tid":1865887,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:08:30.000Z","msg":"元朗西鐵站「連儂牆」1月30日發生襲擊事件，6人受傷送院，其中3名傷者今（6日）在民主派元朗區議員陪同下見傳媒。有傷者表示，當日在連儂牆看防疫「文宣」，先有兩名男子觀察他們，稍後突有7至8名男子加入，重複問「係咪你？」，繼而被對方以金屬伸縮棍及扁鏟圍毆。<br />\n<br />\nB先生表示，當晚10時許用餐後，與朋友經過元朗西鐵站連儂牆附近看防疫文宣，留意到有兩名神情有異的男子，其中一人戴手套，其後有7至8名戴面巾或口罩的男人從對面馬路衝過來，在電梯位截停B先生及其朋友。該批男子指住他們重複問：「係咪你？係咪你？」，B先生沒有回應，施襲者以金屬伸縮棍圍毆他們，令B右邊第12節肋骨斷裂。<br />\n<br />\nC先生及A小姐則目睹該批男子以扁鏟、伸縮棍施襲，一度上前阻止，反遭圍毆。C生生的右額需縫7針，鼻及後腦各縫3針；A小姐遭拳毆頭、臉、背部。<br />\n<br />\n元朗區議會主席黃偉賢稱，原本將此事列入區議會大會議程，但遭民政專員拒絕。另一區議員李頌慈表示，軍裝和便衣警員當晚調查後，有逾60名防暴警察到場「接手」，但他們態度惡劣，現場所有人都要被搜身，追問指揮官獲回覆「佢哋見人多會緊張」，他已向警方投訴。<br />\n<br />\n今日的記者會原於元朗區議會會議室舉行，但民政處職員以防疫為由，拒絕議員以外的人進入會議室，記者會改到升降機大堂舉行，區議員自行搬枱櫈；而民政處職員要求枱櫈要消毒後，才可搬回會議室。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200206/s00001/1580985886920/%e5%85%83%e6%9c%97%e9%80%a3%e5%84%82%e7%89%86%e4%ba%8b%e4%bb%b6-%e6%9c%89%e9%81%87%e8%a5%b2%e8%80%85%e8%82%8b%e9%aa%a8%e6%96%b7%e8%a3%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200206%2Fs00001%2F1580985886920%2F%25e5%2585%2583%25e6%259c%2597%25e9%2580%25a3%25e5%2584%2582%25e7%2589%2586%25e4%25ba%258b%25e4%25bb%25b6-%25e6%259c%2589%25e9%2581%2587%25e8%25a5%25b2%25e8%2580%2585%25e8%2582%258b%25e9%25aa%25a8%25e6%2596%25b7%25e8%25a3%2582&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsn88up93QrsUiEJqOxYGoBw%3D&h=ed6d4700\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200206%2Fs00001%2F1580985886920%2F%25e5%2585%2583%25e6%259c%2597%25e9%2580%25a3%25e5%2584%2582%25e7%2589%2586%25e4%25ba%258b%25e4%25bb%25b6-%25e6%259c%2589%25e9%2581%2587%25e8%25a5%25b2%25e8%2580%2585%25e8%2582%258b%25e9%25aa%25a8%25e6%2596%25b7%25e8%25a3%2582&h=c76a38cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200206/s00001/1580985886920/%e5%85%83%e6%9c%97%e9%80%a3%e5%84%82%e7%89%86%e4%ba%8b%e4%bb%b6-%e6%9c%89%e9%81%87%e8%a5%b2%e8%80%85%e8%82%8b%e9%aa%a8%e6%96%b7%e8%a3%82</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200206/s00001/04e241acfceb6004c332831e64450bd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200206%2Fs00001%2F04e241acfceb6004c332831e64450bd2.jpg&h=5c15bfb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200206/s00001/04bb7afef1f4de2361a2f058950dcfa3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200206%2Fs00001%2F04bb7afef1f4de2361a2f058950dcfa3.jpg&h=16a0b36e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">放心，我有罩都唔會派比元朗國民政事務處任何職員</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a737103b308f268e9d2f48f790da015692275e62","tid":1865887,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:08:55.000Z","msg":"堅尼地城即時<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1865859\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1865859</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"940ef142886e2302d7dcfb3d7252449d7d5f18f2","tid":1865887,"uid":343033,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:11:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ae15df938d0dff9f2cbc94c37206106040ad22f","tid":1865887,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:11:27.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 謝一謝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.